commit.message: added testcases files to reproduce previously reported issues
added note about the original repo
make compile on both msvc and linux
removed getopt submodule, putting it back into the tree

Fix build on systems with split ncurses/tinfo libraries

* Replace AC_CHECK_LIB macros with AC_SEARCH_LIBS
  (https://autotools.io/autoconf/finding.html)
* Add search for `cbreak` in either libncurses or libtinfo
Prevent segfault when buf index is negative.

Update instructions for building from Git

  Mention required Perl modules

Convert to Git

  Update to Autoconf 2.64 (adds PACKAGE_URL)
  Remove $Id$ & $Revision$ tags
  Add configure.commit & post-commit for AC_REVISION
  Add README.md for GitHub
  Bump version to 3.0_beta5

Add --enable-debug option to configure.ac

Update NEWS.tt for 3.0_beta4 release on July 26, 2008
Fix bug in WriteFile (must supply a bytesWritten parameter)

Bump version to 3.0_beta4

Add GPL notice to tables.h, version.h.tt, ConWin.cpp, ConWin.hpp, FileIO.hpp,
  StdAfx.cpp, vbindiff.rc, config.h, & Makefile.am
List http://www.gnu.org/licenses/ instead of the FSF's mailing address
